---
title: Plant-Based Basil Pesto & Courgette Risotto with Almond Pangrattato & Parsley
description: This rich, creamy risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you free to create a quick and crunchy almond pangrattato to sprinkle over at the end. Such a small factor takes this plant-based veggie meal to the next level – taste it and see!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65716c8438e51a4a51a2ffe3-7c738a89.jpeg
